title: Final Audit Report on Lieberman for Vice President is Now Available
html:
FEC HOME > NEWS > NEWS WIRE

July 9, 2002

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:

FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
LIEBERMAN FOR VICE PRESIDENT

The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Lieberman for Vice President. This audit covers the period of August 11, 2000 through December 29, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
